title._content: NSW servicemen portraits, 1918-19 - Rudolph John Schulstad / photographer unknown

description._content: A Happy New Year 2013 from the State Library of New South Wales! In ink on the verso of the postcard: "Aunt Jane, Uncle Bob and Family, Wishing them a Merry Christmas and a Happy New Year, From Aubrey" It was a happy 1919 when he came home in July. Format: Photograph Find more detailed information about this photographic collection: acms.sl.nsw.gov.au/item/itemDetailPaged.aspx?itemID=433312 From the collection of the State Library of New South Wales www.sl.nsw.gov.au
